---
// about.astro — Lance Murphey's origin story, magazine-style.
// Desktop: full-bleed boll weevil monument hero (restored original design).
// Mobile: UNCHANGED from the locked-in version.
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
 
<BaseLayout title="About — Lance Murphey · The Story Speaks">
 
  <main class="about-page">
 
    <!-- ============ HERO: Boll weevil monument, full bleed ============ -->
    <section class="about-hero">
 
      <div class="hero-stage">
        <div class="hero-image"></div>
      </div>
 
      <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
 
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1 class="hero-headline">
         The story<br><span class="gold-italic">behind the story.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-byline">By Lance Murphey</p>
      </div>
 
      <p class="hero-caption">The boll weevil monument in Enterprise, Alabama.</p>
    </section>
 
    <!-- ============ ARTICLE BODY ============ -->
    <article class="about-article">
 
      <p class="lead-paragraph">
        I was 5,000 miles into a story when my phone rang.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        For weeks I'd been driving the back roads of the cotton belt, chasing the boll weevil &mdash; a small insect that crossed the Rio Grande in the early 1900s and destroyed every farm in its path. The story had become an obsession. The boll weevil's path had triggered the Great Migration, sparked the birth of the Blues, and pushed the bald eagle to the brink.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        When my phone rang, I was pulling over to unload my cameras at the side of the road.
      </p>
 
      <div class="dialogue">
        <p>&ldquo;I'm sorry,&rdquo; said my colleague.</p>
        <p>&ldquo;For what?&rdquo;</p>
        <p>&ldquo;Oh sh*t. You haven't heard?&rdquo;</p>
      </div>
 
      <p>
        A few minutes later I sat in the dust at the edge of a cotton field knowing that the photojournalism job I'd held for nearly two decades, the one I'd built my family on, was gone. A week later I drove to the unemployment office and learned the money would not be enough to feed my newborn son.
      </p>
 
      <figure class="image-pair">
        <div class="pair-item">
          <img src="/images/about-crop-duster.jpg" alt="Crop duster biplane silhouetted against a sunset sky over a cotton field, with a boll weevil trap in the foreground" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Crop duster Wade Hargrave flies a biplane over a boll weevil trap near Tallulah, Louisiana.</figcaption>
        </div>
        <div class="pair-item">
          <img src="/images/about-boll-weevil-macro.jpg" alt="Close-up of a boll weevil on the stem of a cotton plant" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>A boll weevil on a cotton plant near the Rio Grande in Brownsville, Texas.</figcaption>
        </div>
      </figure>
 
      <p>
        For twenty years I had carried a camera in pursuit of stories. From the burning ghats of Varanasi, India, to a smuggler's tunnel in Nogales, Mexico. I rode an elephant in pursuit of wild tigers and shattered speed limits in a presidential motorcade. I made pictures for the <em>New York Times</em>, the <em>Washington Post</em>, and <em>TIME</em>. And I was twice honored as Scripps Howard Newspaper Photographer of the Year.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        And then, in a single phone call, it all stopped.
      </p>
 
      <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
 
      <p>
        But the call that changed my life came a few weeks later.
      </p>
 
      <p class="dialogue-single">
        &ldquo;This is the editor of <em>Pumper Magazine</em>. Will you take the cover photograph for our May issue?&rdquo;
      </p>
 
      <p>
        I screamed yes before I knew what <em>Pumper Magazine</em> was. (It is, I learned, the leading trade publication for the liquid waste industry. The May cover was a photo of a septic tank truck.)
      </p>
 
      <p>
        I built a freelance business from there, one truck at a time. The work taught me something I hadn't fully understood before. The most valuable thing I'd brought home from twenty years in newsrooms wasn't a camera or a Rolodex or even my skill at making pictures.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        The most valuable thing was knowing how to find a story. How to recognize the human truth inside any subject &mdash; even a septic tank truck on a back road in early summer.
      </p>
 
      <blockquote class="pull-quote">
        <p>The currency of journalism, honest stories full of universal human truths, turned out to be the most valuable asset I owned.</p>
      </blockquote>
 
      <p>
        What started as a freelance photography business has evolved into The Story Speaks: a strategic film and media company for organizations that need to move people.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        The films I've made since have earned five Emmys, a national ADDY, and recognition from TED as one of 20 Ads Worth Spreading in the world. <em>The Shadow Between Us</em>, a documentary about racial unity made in the wake of George Floyd, won two Emmys and is in national rotation on PBS. I've worked with healthcare systems, research universities, Fortune 500 brands, and nonprofits fighting for things that matter.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        Behind every project, the same instinct: find the story underneath the brief.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        That instinct is what I eventually codified as the PRISM Method &mdash; a five-phase narrative architecture for translating complex truth into resonant human experience. More than a creative process, it's a way of bringing the discipline of journalism into the work of filmmaking. A way of refusing to start with a concept and instead starting with the human moment that makes the rest of the work matter.
      </p>
 
      <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
 
      <figure class="portrait">
        <img src="/images/about-lance-portrait.jpg" alt="Lance Murphey, with the Flatirons of Boulder, Colorado, in the background" loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
 
      <p>
        I live in Boulder, Colorado, with my family. I travel for most of my work.
      </p>
 
      <p>
        If you have a story you're trying to find, or one you can feel the shape of but can't quite tell, I'd love to hear about it. The best films I've ever made started not with a brief but with a conversation. A phone call. Someone telling me about a person, a place, a problem they wanted to give voice to.
      </p>
 
      <p class="closing-line">
        Maybe the next one is yours.
      </p>
 
      <p class="signature">&mdash; Lance Murphey</p>
 
      <div class="cta-wrapper">
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">
          <span>Start a Conversation</span>
          <span class="cta-arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
 
    </article>
 
  </main>
 
</BaseLayout>
 
<style>
  /* ============================================================
     PAGE FRAME
     ============================================================ */
  .about-page {
    background: var(--color-bg-deep, #0a1628);
    color: var(--color-text-primary, #f8fafc);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
 
  /* ============================================================
     HERO — DESKTOP: full-bleed boll weevil monument
     ============================================================ */
  .about-hero {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 88vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
 
  /* hero-stage is an unstyled wrapper on desktop — needed for mobile CSS to work.
     hero-image positions absolutely against .about-hero (the nearest positioned ancestor). */
 .hero-image {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 2.5rem;
  background-image: url('/images/about-boll-weevil-monument-horizontal.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center top%;
  z-index: 0;
}
 
  /* Gradient overlay: subtle vignette top, darker at bottom for headline contrast */
  .hero-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg,
        rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.25) 0%,
        rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.0) 30%,
        rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.4) 70%,
        rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.92) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }
 
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem 0rem 17rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
 
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-wordmark, system-ui);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent, #e8c574);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
 
  .hero-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans, system-ui);
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: clamp(3.25rem, 8.5vw, 6.25rem);
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #f8fafc;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    max-width: 14ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
 
  .hero-headline .gold-italic {
    color: var(--color-accent, #e8c574);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
 
  .hero-byline {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.78);
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
 
  .hero-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.25rem;
    right: 2rem;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.55);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 280px;
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
 
  /* ============================================================
     ARTICLE
     ============================================================ */
  .about-article {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 6rem;
    position: relative;
  }
 
  .about-article p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans, system-ui);
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.25vw, 1.15rem);
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.88);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
 
  .about-article p em,
  .about-article p i {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.95);
  }
 
  .lead-paragraph {
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 1.9vw, 1.65rem) !important;
    line-height: 1.5 !important;
    color: #f8fafc !important;
    font-weight: 300 !important;
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem !important;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
 
  .lead-paragraph::first-letter {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 4.5em;
    line-height: 0.85;
    float: left;
    margin: 0.05em 0.12em 0 -0.05em;
    color: var(--color-accent, #e8c574);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
  }
 
  .dialogue {
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(232, 197, 116, 0.3);
  }
 
  .dialogue p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.85) !important;
  }
 
  .dialogue p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }
 
  .dialogue-single {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(232, 197, 116, 0.3);
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.92) !important;
  }
 
  .image-pair {
    margin: 3.5rem auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    width: calc(100% + 320px);
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin-left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    position: relative;
  }
 
  .pair-item {
    margin: 0;
  }
 
  .pair-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
  }
 
  .pair-item figcaption {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.55);
    margin: 0.85rem 0 0;
    line-height: 1.55;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0 0.25rem;
  }
 
  .pull-quote {
    margin: 4rem auto;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 740px;
    margin-left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
 
  .pull-quote::before,
  .pull-quote::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 25%;
    right: 25%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(232, 197, 116, 0.5), transparent);
  }
  .pull-quote::before { top: 0; }
  .pull-quote::after { bottom: 0; }
 
  .pull-quote p {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif !important;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.4vw, 1.95rem) !important;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    line-height: 1.45 !important;
    color: var(--color-accent, #e8c574) !important;
    margin: 0 auto !important;
    max-width: 32ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
 
  .section-divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(232, 197, 116, 0.6), transparent);
    margin: 3rem auto;
  }
 
  .portrait {
    margin: 3.5rem auto 2.5rem;
    max-width: 380px;
  }
 
  .portrait img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }
 
  .closing-line {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif !important;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 1.5vw, 1.3rem) !important;
    color: var(--color-accent, #e8c574) !important;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem !important;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
  }
 
  .signature {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif !important;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.75) !important;
    margin: 0 0 3rem !important;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
  }
 
  .cta-wrapper {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
 
  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    padding: 1.1rem 2.25rem;
    background: var(--color-accent, #e8c574);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent, #e8c574);
    border-radius: 2px;
    color: var(--color-bg-deep, #0a1628);
    font-family: var(--font-wordmark, system-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(232, 197, 116, 0.25);
  }
 
  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #f0d28d;
    border-color: #f0d28d;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(232, 197, 116, 0.4);
  }
 
  .cta-arrow {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
 
  .cta-button:hover .cta-arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
 
  /* ============================================================
     MOBILE (UNCHANGED — exactly as locked-in)
     ============================================================ */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-hero {
      min-height: 74vh;
    }
 
    /* Mobile: restore full-bleed image (no letterboxing) */
    .hero-stage {
      display: block;
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
    }
 
    .hero-image {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      top: 2rem;
      height: calc(100% - 2rem);
      aspect-ratio: auto;
      background-image: url('/images/about-boll-weevil-monument.jpg');
      background-position: center top;
      box-shadow: none;
    }
 
    .hero-gradient {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg,
          rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.25) 0%,
          rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.0) 30%,
          rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.4) 70%,
          rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.92) 100%);
    }
 
    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 16rem 1.5rem 0rem 3.5rem;
    }
 
    .hero-headline {
      max-width: 5ch;
    }
 
    .hero-caption {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0rem;
      right: 0rem;
      max-width: 6rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem;
      background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
 
    .about-article {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem 4.5rem;
    }
 
    .image-pair {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
      transform: none;
      margin-left: 0;
    }
 
    .pull-quote {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      transform: none;
      margin-left: 0;
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
 
    .pull-quote::before,
    .pull-quote::after {
      left: 15%;
      right: 15%;
    }
 
    .lead-paragraph::first-letter {
      font-size: 4em;
    }
 
    .portrait {
      max-width: 280px;
      margin: 2.5rem auto 2rem;
    }
 
    .cta-button {
      padding: 1rem 1.75rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
  }
 
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-headline {
      font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 11vw, 3rem);
    }
 
    .about-article p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  }
</style>
 
